                        IndexedNonterminal instantiableNonterminal)
        Determines whether there is a materialization and an instantiation such that the indices of the given nonterminals are equal.
        Parameters:
        materializableNonterminal - a nonterminal with a (possibly) abstract index
        instantiableNonterminal - a nonterminal with a (possibly) instantiable index
        Returns:
        true if there is a materialization and an instantiation such that the indices of the given nonterminals are equal.
